column2: SELECT TOP # p.obj,  str(p.ra,#,#) as ra,  str(p.[dec],#,#) as dec,  p.dered_g as g,  p.dered_r as r,  p.dered_i as i,  p.dered_z as z,  str(p.g-p.r, #,#) as gr,   str(p.g-p.i, #,#) as gi,  str(p.r-p.i, #,#) as ri,  p.petroR5#_g,p.petroR5#_r,p.petroR5#_i,  p.petroR9#_g,p.petroR9#_r,p.petroR9#_i,  ISNULL(s.z,#) as zSpec, ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as zErr,  ISNULL(s.zWarning,#) as zWarning,ISNULL(s.class,#) as class,   p.score as score,  c.z,c.zErr FROM photoObj AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) AS b ON b.objID = P.objID  JOIN Photoz AS c ON c.objID = P.objID  WHERE g < # AND r < # AND i < # AND p.z < # AND p.type = # AND c.z > #
